Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} managed to turn the tides\N with a major counterattack against Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But jut as he managed to\N back him into a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik went and Summoned Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Ra's third Hidden Ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s life spirit going\N to burn up along with all his\N Monsters on the field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please! Endure it, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Victory's right in front of your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jounouchi Dies"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop screwing around...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I lose, I'll never see Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...EVER AGAIN!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BURN!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'TILL THE LAST OF YOUR\N LIFE IS BURNED AWAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this goes on, the pain will\N shatter Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s mind...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...!\N This Malik jerk's gone way too far...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi could really die up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ra's third Hidden Ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally saw it with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not bad at all for a deadbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have my respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to me, phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the remainder of his {\i1}soul{\i0}\N rising to Heaven with the smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!!\N He's still {\i1}alive{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is our final match!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Final match...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah... I withstood the attack\N from Malik's Ra back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the next turn, Resurrection of the Dead's\N effect disappeared, and Ra vanished\N from Malik's field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right! And on your next turn,\N you Summoned Gearfried\N and defeated Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! We kept our promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's Duel, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me Jounouchi's willpower\N was {\i1}stronger{\i0} than {\b0}God's attack{\b1}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This {\i1}can't{\i0} be happening...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice endurance, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra disappeared from Malik's field!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he attacks Malik,\N Jounouchi will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He beat {\i1}God{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now play a Monster, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gearfried... The...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resisting to the very end...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now enter into a time count!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounou-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Katsuya Jounouchi is no longer\N able to continue, this Duel is now over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of the first\N Semi-Final match is Malik Ishtar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Jounouchi!\N -Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono!! Call the medical team!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have them take him to the Battle Ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think someone like {\i1}him{\i0}\N pushed me this far...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! JOUNOUCHI~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...! Wake up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, brother! Big brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU BASTARD!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doctor...! Is a doctor here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on their way right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAMMIT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a lie...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}IT'S A LIE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In your death...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll accept you as a Duelist\N as you come to your end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet {\i1}another{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another sacrifice to the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another being has\N vanished from this world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} isn't dead yet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big deal~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He {\i1}shall{\i0} be very {\i1}shortly{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's death {\i1}wasn't{\i0} in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For {\i1}me{\i0}, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik... You showed me everything\N in your Duel with Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen all of Ra's Abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the key to defeating God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lies in this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I wish you the {\i1}best{\i0} of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Carry him to the Medical Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Big brother!\N -Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\N -Just hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Don't die!\N -Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\N -Stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Duel of the Semi-Finals\N will take place in one hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overcome your friend's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and return to this Duel Arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be waiting for you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, how's Jounouchi doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His vital signs have\N improved slightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to be frank, he's in a\N very dangerous condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dangerous condition"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Jounouchi... going to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Isn't this Domino City...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Old man Sugoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, we've been looking\N all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What in the world\N are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-H-Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-Where are we going, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean, "where"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it obvious we're going to the\N Domino City District Duel Tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}District Duel Tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we don't hurry up,\N the tournament will start without us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So pick up the pace, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're going to be disqualified\N if you don't get there in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I entered in the\N District Duel Tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man, Honda,\N makes only one request!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save him! Please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know\N what is causing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a {\i1}doctor{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your {\i1}job{\i0} to cure sick people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Power of Darkness is what\N is causing his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Modern medicine can't\N do anything for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only hope we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is that this boy has the willpower\N necessary to pull through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even if I {\i1}did{\i0} know what\N was wrong with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the equipment\N here to treat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to transfer him to\N a proper hospital immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take him on the Battle Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go ask them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't take him\N there on this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! You're still saying shit\N like that at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a {\i1}damn{\i0} about these\N Duels when someone's life is on the line!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We {\i1}can't{\i0} fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't {\i1}fly{\i0}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's engine is broken...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened when we escaped\N from Noah's mobile fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That struggle destroyed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily we made it\N to Alcatraz in one piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the engine won't even start...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should at least be able to call\N Kaiba Corporation for a helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the trouble, Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't tell my brother, alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't die...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... fight anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, when I win this tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when the time comes where I can call myself a True Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When that time comes, please fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll fight each other then, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The promise I made that day\N was supposed to be my main\N objective in Battle City...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My lost memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The God Cards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They should have been {\b0}nothing{\b1} compared to the promise I made with my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite that... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I sacrifice Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}\N for things like {\b0}that{\b1}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only thing keeping me going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is my hatred for Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will I have left {\b0}then{\b1}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attack Holograh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Booyah! I win!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}YEEEAHH~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The District Duel Tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looking back on it, that may have\N been the first step I took on my\N way to becoming a True Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die on me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to ask you\N what a {\b0}True{\b1} Duelist is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Tauk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the Millennium Item\N Ishizu-{\i0}san{\i1} gave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This belonged to you originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Ishizu said the\N Millennium Tauk is losing its power...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why is it glowing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! Our Battle City isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That vision just now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Millennium Tauk should have\N lost its powers, but it showed me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our future...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will now begin the second\N Duel of the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will the participating Duelists please report\N to the stage atop the Duel Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll believe in this future!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'll fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please respond, Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send a helicopter to Alcatraz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all! What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible there is temporary disturbance\N due to the explosion that missile caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mokuba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please respond, Kaiba Corporation!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed to the Duel Ring\N where Kaiba's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you stay here and keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a {\i1}Duelist{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you guys to stay here\N with Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying Dueling is more\N important than Jounouchi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to fight\N at a time like {\i1}this{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Jounouchi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even that man named Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of them have fallen\N one after the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got nothing {\i1}left{\i0} to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fight because I\N promised Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promised...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Millennium Tauk showed\N me a vision of the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I run from this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that future will never come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the Egyptian slab in\N the Domino Museum, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why is there a carving of Yugi on that stone tablet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu, I have just realized who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The soul of an Ancient Egyptian Pharaoh - \Na king who was trapped inside the\N Millennium Puzzle for thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}That{\b1} is who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul was supposed to\N have been lost long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am alive,\N existing right here in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came back to find what I've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people continue\N to search for answers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they have a reason to live,\N a place to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} will come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain he'll return to us\N as his usual, energetic self!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}believe{\i0} in that future!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win this, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I lose Yugi, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to make my\N promise to you a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So don't you lose either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will fight as a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believing in his future with Jounouchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi meets Kaiba atop the Duel Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They head further down the road paved by everyone in Battle City.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It becomes a battle of fate as they fight for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi pits the Osiris he holds against the Obelisk Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's become a battle of the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A fierce battle is starting, with their pride on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Sky Colosseum:\N Yugi VS Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.91,0:23:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
